  ('investigation-2b298e71-moex-00001', 'investigation-2b298e71', 'investigation-2b298e71-moex-114-de0a21a2', 'sub-investigation-2b298e71-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲長期將鞋子、燒金紙用的金桶等雜物，靠牆放置在其居住公寓的樓梯
